  <description><![CDATA[<p>The perfect skier’s hotel, the Furggen is directly on the piste so you can ski down to the lifts and right back to the hotel at the end of the day. It offers an informal and relaxed atmosphere, with a spacious lounge/bar and superb views over the village. The centre of Cervinia is a 15 minute walk, but the hotel provides a free shuttle bus in the evening from 5-11.30pm (not available on 31 Dec).</p>]]></description>
